title: Made "Tint from Wallpaper" a button since it acted like one anyway.  (and will…
message:
Made "Tint from Wallpaper" a button since it acted like one anyway.  (and will change significantly in 1.5)

We now create the ColorTheme table at install when not an upgrade so fresh installs actually work.
